{"tid":841142,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣布 埋大成為紅底大學","createTime":"2018-09-29T11:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T19:09:50.000Z","uid":27697,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"40eeb62983f4a28627b76467d50a8a921e069d06","tid":841142,"uid":27697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T11:12:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/305868249479813/posts/1929760603757228/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F305868249479813%2Fposts%2F1929760603757228%2F&d=zGo0cuoyrN46cO%2BC553fq49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=66d273bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/305868249479813/posts/1929760603757228/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/191021_2254d9ba420f1e52d5014d57d8f49ed5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F191021_2254d9ba420f1e52d5014d57d8f49ed5.png&h=e4253ae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【校園即時】 校方疑收回民主牆     「連儂牆」被紅紙遮住<br />\n<br />\n幹事會昨日於校方延長的限期前（9月28日18：30）於民主牆張貼舊的守則（針對民主牆之管理守則），以及於便利貼蓋上學生會的印章（針對民主牆之用途），理論上符合民主牆之原有守則，惟編委於今早發現 「連儂牆」被紅紙遮住，上面貼上民主牆的舊守則，並加上由校方後加的備註：<br />\n除文義另有所指外，在香港理工大學管理民主牆期間：<br />\n1）民主牆使用規條4 提到 &ldquo;幹事會&rdquo; 是指 &ldquo;香港理工大學&rdquo;。<br />\n2）在民主牆使用規條的其他地方提到 &ldquo;幹事會&rdquo; 或 &ldquo;香港理工大學學生會&rdquo; 是指 &ldquo;香港理工大學學生發展處&rdquo; 。<br />\n<br />\n編委向幹事會查詢， 幹事會表示沒有於「連儂牆」蓋上紅紙，並將作內部討論商討對策。<br />\n<br />\n理大學務長莫志明教授昨日於與學生會的會會議上表明，如果幹事會未能還原民主牆，校方將拆掉「連儂牆」，並問幹事會該如何處理牆上的絲帶和便利貼。<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：<br />\n【校園即時】 理工大學擬沒收民主牆 「連儂牆」便利貼疑於深夜被撕毀 <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1927013814031907&amp;id=305868249479813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1927013814031907%26id%3D305868249479813&d=zGo0cuoyrN46cO%2BC553fq49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e7d3a79a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1927013814031907&amp;id=305868249479813</a><br />\n<br />\n【校園即時】 未拆「連儂牆」 先拆雨革橫額<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/305868249479813/posts/1927627883970500/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F305868249479813%2Fposts%2F1927627883970500%2F&d=zGo0cuoyrN46cO%2BC553fq49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=beeb315f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/305868249479813/posts/1927627883970500/</a><br />\n<br />\n【編委報導】理大「連儂牆」被勒令還原 幹事會批判校方做法無理<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1927953633937925&amp;id=305868249479813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1927953633937925%26id%3D305868249479813&d=zGo0cuoyrN46cO%2BC553fq49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=309f80eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1927953633937925&amp;id=305868249479813</a><br />\n<br />\n【編委報導】莫志明教授：民主牆唔係畀你哋講啲咁敏感嘅嘢<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1929292990470656&amp;id=305868249479813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1929292990470656%26id%3D305868249479813&d=zGo0cuoyrN46cO%2BC553fq49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=7528aac2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1929292990470656&amp;id=305868249479813</a>"},{"pid":"c37c7243cbb3e48eb4fd2938aedd93ff5b72ff35","tid":841142,"uid":61853,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"民主牆唔民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586ff79d54d6c83a6f2765472ae27b42aef0c974","tid":841142,"uid":3874,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T11:24:48.000Z","msg":"依家變撚咗國旗 左上比人痴咗五粒星<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9127c09feea9c2094e4bcbaa9493a85db95b29c2","tid":841142,"uid":199869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedB